NumTSModelSet.name: Variation of N cars by 15-min intervals *50: daily and weekly
NumTSModelSet.Annotation: This is a model of the standard traffic depending on time of the day and day of the week. It predicts how many cars will be in each place by 15-min time intervals within a given time period. The data have been obtained by aggregating GPS tracks of cars and scaling by factor 50 (i.e. the sample of the tracked cars is estimated as 2% of the total number of cars in the city).
